  "detailed_description": "<h1>Great on Steam Deck!</h1><p>Full controller support and optimized graphical performance makes this game an excellent choice for playing on the go on your Steam Deck or other handheld device!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/3f9fbdfb3ea66dab7c6ebc22cee4898b.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Code your vehicle with a series of commands to complete various courses, tasks, stunts, and races in this physics-based brain teasing racing puzzle game!<br><br>Program your way through over 100 exciting levels featuring challenging puzzles, tight turns, big jumps, moving platforms, giant balls and more in over 30 different vehicles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feeling good about your skills? Compete against the world in online code races to see who's the fastest programmer!<br><br>Take on the Daily Challenge for a chance to win big and try out unique levels that you havnt unlocked yet!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have an old or slow device? No worries, Code Racer features optimized graphics that make performance smooth on any device!<br><br>Great for kids and adults alike as an intro to a programming mind-set and STEM problem solving!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/3f9fbdfb3ea66dab7c6ebc22cee4898b.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Code your vehicle with a series of commands to complete various courses, tasks, stunts, and races in this physics-based brain teasing racing puzzle game!<br><br>Program your way through over 100 exciting levels featuring challenging puzzles, tight turns, big jumps, moving platforms, giant balls and more in over 30 different vehicles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/92d47fcf86bf48a18022d63fd655ebf3.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feeling good about your skills? Compete against the world in online code races to see who's the fastest programmer!<br><br>Take on the Daily Challenge for a chance to win big and try out unique levels that you havnt unlocked yet!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/c43193e60d30ef61279af7f4c875d1d8.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have an old or slow device? No worries, Code Racer features optimized graphics that make performance smooth on any device!<br><br>Great for kids and adults alike as an intro to a programming mind-set and STEM problem solving!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.poster.avif?t=1709755194\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.webm?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808360/extras/a6cf3c3b9e98d004b3e0b4189e63e8f6.mp4?t=1709755194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
